, "outline": {"ch": "1.學生將能夠簡單介紹家庭及使用對家人的稱呼。\n2.學生將能夠學會在日常生活購物中使用百以上的大數字。\n3.學生將能夠簡單表達個人喜好和能力。\n4.學生將能夠簡單表達地點、位置和行為動作。", "en": "1.Students will be able to simply introduce family members and titles. comment the result of an action as well as to simply describe personal or others’ hobbies.\n2.Students will be able to simply use numbers great than or equal to 100 for daily convenient shopping.\n3.Students will be able to simply express individual preferences and abilities.\n4.Students will be able to simply express places, locations and movements."}, "textbook": {"ch": "新版實用視聽華語1（正中書局）", "en": "Practical Audio-Visual Chinese 1 (3rd Edition, Chen Chung Book Ca., LTD.)"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "20%", "en": "20%"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n\n\n個別指導\n其他", "en": ["Lecture", "", "", "Individual Instruction", "Others"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "出席：10％\n課堂表現：30％\n平時測驗與小考：15％\n作業練習：15％\n期中口筆試：15％\n期末筆試與期末報告：15％", "en": "Attendance : 10％\nClass Participation: 30％\nQuizzes and Tests: 15％\nHomework: 15％\nMid-term exam: 15％\nFinal exam and presentation: 15％"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "每週二下午4:30到5:30或另外約時間", "en": "Tuesday afternoon 4:30-5:30 or by appointment"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "18", "en": "18"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "domain": {"ch": "華語教學", "en": "華語教學"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "語言溝通", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現", "學習檔案評量", "作品/創作展演", "其他"]}, {"competencies": "文化視野", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現", "學習檔案評量", "作品/創作展演", "其他"]}, {"competencies": "自主學習", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現", "學習檔案評量", "其他"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Language & Communication Skills", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Assignments", "Presentation/Oral Exam", "Attendance/Performance", "Portfolios Assessment", "Products/Creative Performance", "Others"]}, {"competencies": "Intercultural Literacy", "rating": "(4)High", "a